{"type": "article", "id": 29132, "title": "可口可乐款Herschel包包不错，以及，大量秀场图片发布｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-07-05T02:40:52Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [{"id": 1027, "name": "彩妆"}, {"id": 1124, "name": "巴黎"}, {"id": 3018, "name": "高级定制"}, {"id": 5263, "name": "罗马"}, {"id": 12089, "name": "女装"}, {"id": 14026, "name": "度假系列"}, {"id": 29790, "name": "罗马许愿池"}, {"id": 325, "name": "Fendi"}, {"id": 334, "name": "优衣库"}, {"id": 671, "name": "Gucci"}, {"id": 766, "name": "香奈儿"}, {"id": 916, "name": "任天堂"}, {"id": 1582, "name": "爱马仕"}, {"id": 2114, "name": "Bottega Veneta"}, {"id": 2180, "name": "Dolce&Gabbana"}, {"id": 2200, "name": "Moschino"}, {"id": 19485, "name": "Hypebeast"}, {"id": 11530, "name": "宫本茂"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160705101634A5bfWKkiGPCLhqB4.jpg", "contents": "<h3>一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/patrizio-di-marco-dolce-gabbana-board-10479391/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Gucci 前 CEO 加入 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 董事会</b></a>｜Gucci 前董事长兼 CEO Patrizio di Marco 确认加入意大利奢侈品牌 Dolce &amp; Gabbana 董事会，同时担任独立顾问。1 月他从 Gucci 离职时就有消息称他在结束一年期的竞业禁止协议后将加入 Dolce &amp; Gabbana。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/human-resources/moschino-general-manager-gabriele-maggio-10479137/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Moschino 任命新总经理</b></a>｜Moschino  昨日宣布由 Gabriele Maggio 担任总经理一职，接替 Corrado Masini ，即刻生效。49 岁的 Maggio 过去六年在 Gucci 工作，以及在 Bottega Veneta 任职超过六年，将利用他的国际商业及行销经验帮助 Moschino 进行扩张。</p><p><a href=\"http://m.us.fashionmag.com/news/Fendi-marks-90-years-with-Trevi-Fountain-show,710037.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>Fendi 将在罗马许愿池办秀</b></a>｜为庆祝品牌成立 90 周年，Fendi 于近日宣布将在品牌发源地意大利罗马举行一系列的庆祝活动，包括 7 月 7 日在罗马许愿池（Trevi Fountain）发布时装秀。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/runway/resort-2017/paris/hermes/review/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Hermès 2017 度假系列</a>：</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><p></p><figure style=